						<p>This is not dated and refers itself to the reign of the Bāṇa king <hi rend="bold">Māvali-Vāṇarasa</hi> and mentions the same raid by Mudunda of Minki on <hi rend="bold">Kuruṁjiyaḷa</hi> during which the hero Ālamārān <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kelemūḻdan is stated to have fought and died.</p>						

